<br>
<i>We've not only responded to this, I'm even pretty sure it's in the FAQ. The answer is, no one can agree on what an 'RP' server would be, or what we'd enforce or change to make it (or EQ in general) more of an RP game. I can tell you what I'd do to make EQ more of an RP game, but I'm sure many of you would respond quite negatively to my ideas.<br>
<br>
But, hey, here are just a few: <br>
<br>
1. Implement Trivial Combat code everywhere<br>
2. Eliminate the common tongue<br>
3. Allow only one character per server<br>
4. Disallow Paladins grouping with Shadow Knights, etc.<br>
5. Make it so evil races cannot communicate with good, and vice versa. <br>
<br>
Anyway, those are just off the top of my head. Those would make EQ more of a role-playing game in my opinion. But I bet a lot of people will really disagree with me, and of course I need to type in a big disclaimer here: these are just my opinions and are not changes coming to an EQ near you. </i><br>
<br>
My thoughts are count me in!  I'd leave Tarew Marr behind if this server went live.  I'd also add a sixth and seventh restriction... 6) restrict /tell and /gsay to the zone you are in and 7) add guild hall bulletin boards to various building in towns... these boards would allow guild members a common forum to use in the game aside from the horribly implemented /tell and /gsay commands of corruption we presently use (i.e., the system by which one or two power-throng guilds farm all the high end mobs week after week).<br>
<br>
Bring back true role play.<br>
<br>
After reading what Brad thought would make a good role play server all I can say is... another Guiness for me and Brad here! WooT!<br>
<br>
MAKE THIS SERVER LIVE PLEASE!<br>
<br>
- Quip Quarrel <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousecontractsbountiesjobsquestsetc.showMessage?topicID=2146.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousecontractsbountiesjobsquestsetc.showMessage?topicID=2153.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousecontractsbountiesjobsquestsetc.emailToFriend?topicID=2158.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousecontractsbountiesjobsquestsetc.threadControl?topicID=2158.topic><img src=http://www.evercrack.net/shpics/closeThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousecontractsbountiesjobsquestsetc.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=2158.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousecontractsbountiesjobsquestsetc.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=2158.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub35.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion">Main Lounge<option value="thesafehousecontractsbountiesjobsquestsetc">News Bulletin<option value="thesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies">Training Studio<option value="thesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers">The Back Alley<option value="thesafehousefrm13">Quests of Norrath<option value="thesafehousetherootcellar"